Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.92,0:00:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard the conversation.\NYou want to go to the research facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.92,0:00:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You have all the more reason\Nnot to cause troubles.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.63,0:00:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.83,0:00:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Before you start opposing your superior,\Nyou must act like an obedient soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.71,0:00:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you willing to help me get to Naomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.21,0:00:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly. After all, she is one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.75,0:00:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll gather information about the facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.08,0:00:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,For the time being,\Nbehave and carry out your mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.83,0:00:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I found him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi is in the underground tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.96,0:00:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been brought onto a car.\NI don't know where they are headed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.96,0:00:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If Nagi is really there,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.96,0:00:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,if he's still alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.42,0:00:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I must talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.00,0:01:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.92,0:01:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.50,0:01:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.08,0:01:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.13,0:02:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,SCARLET NEXUS
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.17,0:02:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♫A crime in reality♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.50,0:02:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,♫For Heaven's sake♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.75,0:02:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Accepts any fake♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.71,0:02:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,♫And disappears piling the eternity in fantasy♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.25,0:02:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Won't take it at all, I get sick♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.63,0:02:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,♫A girl looking back♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.67,0:02:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Casts the miracle into the instant world♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.00,0:02:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Did you lie♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.96,0:02:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Did you lie♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.83,0:02:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Spit the venom♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.96,0:02:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I know why♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.67,0:02:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I've found a game of ecstasy♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.33,0:02:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Red Criminal gets life♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.83,0:02:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I've never been in love♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.38,0:02:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Don’t know when I started\Ngetting sick of this world♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.17,0:02:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,♫We will fly♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.83,0:02:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Someday I won't be crying♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.46,0:03:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I've been sacrificing myself\Nnot to hurt anybody♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.38,0:03:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,TRUTH HIDDEN IN THE HOSPITAL
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.92,0:03:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,ALERT
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Great, we finally found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.54,0:03:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.63,0:03:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.54,0:03:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.54,0:03:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.04,0:03:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.54,0:03:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.50,0:03:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We just want to know what happened to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.42,0:03:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No one will blame you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.71,0:03:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So you want to know...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.92,0:03:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have no idea either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.25,0:04:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,My mind went blank.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.71,0:04:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It was as though someone\Nwas stirring up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.54,0:04:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.42,0:04:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, you must leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.71,0:04:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You must get out of this place now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.00,0:04:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll buy you some time. Just run!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.42,0:04:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll fight by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.00,0:04:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.58,0:04:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even know when I'll turn on you\Nand kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.71,0:04:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.00,0:04:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.38,0:04:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I will stop you for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.25,0:04:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You will become just like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.25,0:04:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No, they might turn you into Others!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Turned into Others?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.04,0:05:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yuito, I'm sorry.\N-Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.42,0:05:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.96,0:05:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I can no longer be part of the team.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.00,0:05:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.75,0:05:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.79,0:06:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Luka, why did you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.92,0:06:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you weren't thinking straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.29,0:06:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.63,0:06:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We should leave this place at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.83,0:06:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.96,0:06:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We now know about the government's secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.54,0:06:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too dangerous to stay here any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.00,0:06:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.71,0:06:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-They come in great number.\N-Yuito, run while you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.67,0:06:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He took out those monsters on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.67,0:06:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This is impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.33,0:06:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like the experiment went well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.67,0:06:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Our effort was worth it after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.29,0:06:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Get to a shelter!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.13,0:07:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The Others were waiting to ambush us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.17,0:07:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everyone all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.04,0:07:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Major General Fubuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.83,0:07:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No one was hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.92,0:07:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.58,0:07:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are contacting us,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.71,0:07:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,that means the government knows\Nabout our operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.71,0:07:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.08,0:07:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The government is discussing your punishments.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.17,0:07:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So you knew all along
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.17,0:07:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,why Nagi was taken to that place?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.88,0:07:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.46,0:07:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It was my responsibility\Nthat he was turned into that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.33,0:07:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.21,0:07:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.83,0:07:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,is used to brainwash anyone who would
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.71,0:07:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,go against the government.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi witnessed Naomi's metamorphosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.29,0:08:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That was why he was taken there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.92,0:08:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't get the same treatment because\NI took it upon myself to monitor you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.33,0:08:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But before that, Nagi was already taken there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.29,0:08:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-I see.\N-Nagi was hurt and brought to a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.21,0:08:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That was when they did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.67,0:08:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.42,0:08:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could have found out sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.71,0:08:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't your fault, Major General Fubuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.33,0:08:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,May I ask,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.50,0:08:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,what do you mean about Naomi's metamorphosis?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.13,0:08:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't she killed in action?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.67,0:08:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.08,0:08:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Naomi didn't die a soldier\Nbut was turned into a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.38,0:08:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Naomi was turned into Other?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.46,0:08:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll start from the very beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.75,0:08:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But as a member of the Ichijo family,\NI hope you don't overreact.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.17,0:08:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.17,0:08:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.58,0:09:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,is the New Himuka government's\Nresearch facility
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.04,0:09:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,to conduct brain power experiments.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.92,0:09:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They make adjustments to the brain\Nto draw out greater power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.71,0:09:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,However, there are two side effects.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Rehabilitation, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.96,0:09:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.71,0:09:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The other side effect is metamorphosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.75,0:09:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Contacting certain materials
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.79,0:09:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,will trigger the metamorphosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.33,0:09:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Any creature with a brain
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.96,0:09:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,will turn into Other.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.17,0:09:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.33,0:09:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mean the culprit that turned Naomi\Ninto a monster
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.38,0:09:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,was the government all along?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.42,0:09:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,People will start to suspect\Nif this conversation went on any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.58,0:09:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll send you the next order.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.92,0:09:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Before that, stand by.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.54,0:09:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Major General Fubuki,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.33,0:09:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,why didn't the government do anything to you\Neven when you know their secrets?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.54,0:09:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.17,0:09:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm siding with the system.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.67,0:09:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm their lapdog.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.88,0:10:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Luka had learned a great deal from Karen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.04,0:10:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You could ask him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Luka, was everything\NMajor General Fubuki told us
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.00,0:10:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,true?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.50,0:10:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he was telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.33,0:10:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.21,0:10:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a woman by the name Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.38,0:10:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice was the former hospital Chief's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.96,0:10:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She was also the fiancee of Major General Fubuki\Nfrom Spring Pharmaceuticals.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.96,0:10:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Auntie Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.21,0:10:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If I remember correctly,\Nshe was scouted into the force.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.92,0:10:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But she was killed in action.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.67,0:10:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.79,0:10:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,was turned into Other.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.17,0:10:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it the government's doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.25,0:10:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I heard there was an accident during\None of the operations.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.13,0:10:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But still,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.71,0:11:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,how did she turn into Other?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.38,0:11:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother and Fubuki started investigating.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.00,0:11:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,During the process,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.96,0:11:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,they found out the government was conducting\Nrehabilitation and metamorphosis experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.83,0:11:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a surveillance system\Nthroughout all major cities.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.96,0:11:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If the project was conducted by the government,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.33,0:11:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,did my father know too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.21,0:11:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.00,0:11:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's best to assume all central executives\Nknow about the experiments.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.83,0:11:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So my brother knows too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Only I was kept in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.96,0:11:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Major General Spring?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.88,0:11:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I was told your subordinates did something\Nthat would cause us trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.13,0:11:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I am here for.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.96,0:12:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Naomi is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.17,0:12:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you want to join me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.50,0:12:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I might get you into troubles.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.92,0:12:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I am yours to command as long as\NI can be of service for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.46,0:12:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-I am...\N-Come on, Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.83,0:12:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We are your friends.\NHave some trust in us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.42,0:12:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,-I...\N-We're throwing out lives away like lunatics.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.17,0:12:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I not surprised at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.33,0:12:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-I...\N-I will follow you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.50,0:12:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Using the information Arashi gathered,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.21,0:12:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I've prepared the safest routes for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.63,0:12:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Haruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.13,0:12:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We're counting on you for navigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.63,0:12:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.38,0:12:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiden, aren't you coming with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.17,0:12:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get working.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.46,0:13:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is bleak.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.42,0:13:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks too spooky.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.04,0:13:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We need a password.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.58,0:13:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruka, can you bypass it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.17,0:13:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, there is no useful data I can use.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.83,0:13:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Everything has a flaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.79,0:13:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You actually unlocked it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.71,0:13:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable. We didn't know you could do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.25,0:13:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Seiran's security isn't something\Nto write home about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.63,0:13:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this an Other research facility?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.79,0:13:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does it look like a factory?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.71,0:13:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention the stench.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.38,0:13:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unbearable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.58,0:13:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What are they producing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.38,0:14:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.13,0:14:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what these are?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.71,0:14:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,These ampoules
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.00,0:14:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,are the same as the ampoule
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.75,0:14:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,a Seiran soldier dropped after turning Naomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.96,0:14:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.63,0:14:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I once saw these at my home\Nwhen I was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.08,0:14:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,When we talk about the Randalls,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.50,0:14:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Randall Industries comes to mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.29,0:14:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they connected to the ampoules as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.67,0:14:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.71,0:14:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not sure either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.50,0:14:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There are too many uncertainties.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.00,0:14:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Arashi, tell us before you act.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.04,0:14:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The basics of spy operation
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.79,0:14:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,are to acquire information\Nin the shortest amount of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.83,0:14:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive, Arashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.54,0:14:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The security system might as well\Nbe non-existent before you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.38,0:14:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't want her as my enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.50,0:14:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.04,0:14:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,She might dig up all the dirt from your past.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.33,0:14:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I can hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.71,0:15:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps I should do you a favor and\Nstart digging up dirt on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.75,0:15:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Arashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.33,0:15:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.71,0:15:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, run toward ten o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.75,0:15:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.00,0:15:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.08,0:15:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this Alice's Wonderland?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.88,0:15:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. We look tiny in this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.42,0:16:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.04,0:16:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it, my sister is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.96,0:16:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.25,0:16:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.00,0:16:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane! I know you want to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.92,0:16:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But please calm down a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.71,0:16:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.92,0:16:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This voice, it's my sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.25,0:16:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.79,0:16:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.67,0:16:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.04,0:16:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It really is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.96,0:16:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really Kasane?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.92,0:16:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can brain talk with Naomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.88,0:16:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,She must be close.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.33,0:16:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I've detected Naomi's presence.\NIt's behind the door on the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.13,0:16:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be there at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.71,0:16:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane! Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.38,0:16:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't open it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.33,0:17:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, don't come any closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.79,0:17:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.33,0:17:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.79,0:17:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the form she lives in now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.54,0:17:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this Naomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.63,0:17:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.83,0:17:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You became this for saving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.38,0:17:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right, Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.33,0:17:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I could save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.79,0:18:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.50,0:18:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.79,0:18:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.92,0:18:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm alive now because you saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.04,0:18:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's more than I can ask for.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.08,0:18:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I was worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.75,0:18:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why were you worried about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.63,0:18:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I should be worried.\NI should have protected you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.29,0:18:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You are always too dense.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.08,0:18:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I must protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.50,0:18:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That was mean, Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.92,0:18:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But in the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.25,0:18:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.58,0:18:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane, Naomi would be sad\Nif you kept apologizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.50,0:18:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.75,0:18:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If you truly care about Naomi,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.79,0:18:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,this reunion is the best you can ask for\Nfor the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.75,0:19:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We have the location now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.58,0:19:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Kyoka, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.46,0:19:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm now this monstrosity...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.38,0:19:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.58,0:19:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you hurt or ill?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.29,0:19:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Did anyone here bully you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.00,0:19:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.17,0:19:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when I'm Other,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.25,0:19:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,people still treat me well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.17,0:19:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.54,0:19:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But after the ampoule's effect wears off,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.92,0:19:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,it becomes to painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.25,0:19:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be able to communicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.63,0:19:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.04,0:19:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Please,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.21,0:19:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,do not come here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.17,0:19:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Please forget about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.25,0:19:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister, I've finally found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.79,0:19:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally reunite with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.13,0:19:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The ampoule's effect is wearing off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.33,0:20:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.79,0:20:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, leave this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.17,0:20:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave while you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.04,0:20:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane, if you care about Naomi,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.08,0:20:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,you must leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.21,0:20:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.58,0:20:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as I expected, you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.13,0:20:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I suspect we've been toyed\Nby Major General Karen all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.67,0:20:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Naomi can retain her consciousness\Nwith the help of the ampoule.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.38,0:20:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is only a temporary solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.13,0:21:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a way to make her normal again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.75,0:21:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,For that, I need your brain power.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.63,0:21:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My power?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.00,0:21:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Before everything is ready,\Nplease be patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.04,0:21:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Naomi will be safe during this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.00,0:21:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Keeping information from each other\Nis a good way to bring distrust.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.75,0:21:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Make yourself clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.54,0:21:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I have one question for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.42,0:21:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What was the material used to make
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.96,0:21:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,the ampoule you injected Naomi with?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.88,0:21:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, you came back safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.04,0:21:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Major General Fubuki helped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.25,0:21:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Was he the one who persuaded\NChief Sumeragi for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.67,0:21:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It took a great deal of effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.58,0:21:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But if this happened again,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.96,0:21:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,it would be hard to appease him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.92,0:21:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Be mindful of your actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.88,0:21:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.42,0:22:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.08,0:22:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,this is from the OSF hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.58,0:22:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They want Captain Yuito to have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.33,0:22:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.96,0:22:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We left the hospital before we got the medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.25,0:22:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So they sent it here instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.96,0:22:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.33,0:22:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I don't need to let fate dictate me♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.00,0:22:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Because I believe that I can rewrite it♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.71,0:22:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I'll always be a dreamer now and forever♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.21,0:23:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Another sunrise shines now and it blacks out♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.75,0:23:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,♫What's waiting for us at the world's end♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.83,0:23:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Forever eternal, keep the fire going♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.83,0:23:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Who can shake us♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.21,0:23:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Who can define us♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.63,0:23:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,♫It's nothing less than our story♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.58,0:23:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Forever eternal,\Nkeep the fire going in your heart♫
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.75,0:24:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,THE DUBIOUS AMPOULE
